com.amplifyframework.predictions.aws

Class AWSPredictionsPluginConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplifyframework.predictions.aws.AWSPredictionsPluginConfiguration

  • public final class AWSPredictionsPluginConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
    Configuration options for the AWSPredictionsPlugin. Contains settings for different types of predictions operations as well as their network policy.
